      <ID>138</ID>
      <DefaultText>Isalu and Jaelyn stare at you in slowly mounting horror. Jaelyn is the first to her feet, but Isalu is quicker to reach the entrance. She shoulders the other woman aside as the two of them flee the Necropolis, their frantic footsteps echoing from the valley walls as they run.

