      <ID>146</ID>
      <DefaultText>"No, but it sounds like an old name. We have little interest in the dead, unfortunately. You could try asking Oddwald the Sane, though the asking may require extreme patience. We found him in the tomb reached by the code 5-1-4-3."</DefaultText>
